Bug ID: BUG001

Title: Login accepts empty password

Module: Login

Severity: High

Priority: High

Steps to Reproduce:

1. Open Login page
2. Enter valid email
3. Leave password blank
4. Click Login

Expected Result:
Validation message should appear.

Actual Result:
Form is submitted without validation.

Status:
Open

