Bug ID: BUG002

Title: Search box accepts special characters

Module: Product Search

Severity: Medium

Priority: Medium

Steps to Reproduce:

1. Open Products page
2. Enter @#$%^&* in search box
3. Click Search

Expected Result:
Validation message or no results found.

Actual Result:
Unexpected results displayed.

Status:
Open

