Bug ID: BUG003

Title: Cart page layout breaks on mobile view

Module: Cart

Severity: Low

Priority: Low

Steps to Reproduce:

1. Open Cart page on mobile screen
2. Observe product table

Expected Result:
Page should display properly.

Actual Result:
Content overlaps and is not aligned.

